14 TO RECOGNIZE APRIL 7, 2025, AS THE DAY
15 OF LOVE IN THE STATE OF ARKANSAS.
16
17 WHEREAS, working together in a spirit of love bridges gaps created by
18 differing beliefs and improves daily life in work, schools, politics,
19 families, and communities; and
20
21 WHEREAS, highlighting our similarities rather than our differences,
22 such as the common desire for life, liberty, and the pursuit of happiness as
23 outlined in our nation's Declaration of Independence, leads to a feeling of
24 connection and love among citizens regardless of their ages, races, beliefs,
25 or backgrounds; and
26
27 WHEREAS, working together cooperatively and in-person in the
28 performance of acts of service to achieve common goals also helps reinforce
29 feelings of love and acceptance in the communities of Arkansas, more closely
30 bonding our citizens; and
31
32 WHEREAS, there is nothing that cannot be accomplished by the citizens
33 of Arkansas when all come together in a spirit of love,
34
35 NOW THEREFORE,
36 BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES OF THE NINETY-FIFTH GENERAL
